96
00:05:47,309 --> 00:05:49,348
There's nothing like that.
It's a mistake.

97
00:05:49,629 --> 00:05:50,588
Take a look.

98
00:05:50,948 --> 00:05:51,880
No way.

99
00:05:53,028 --> 00:05:53,948
For general hospitals,

100
00:05:54,549 --> 00:05:57,109
