109
00:06:21,629 --> 00:06:22,588
It wasn't like this.

110
00:06:22,908 --> 00:06:24,189
You got it and it went wrong?

111
00:06:24,789 --> 00:06:26,588
You know very well what you did.

112
00:06:28,588 --> 00:06:29,629
